title: MAR 10 2022 - WAR IN UKRAINE - DAY 15 UPDATE
description:
A White House staffer reveals to HED that President Biden and Vice President Harris are not talking, that the administration is clueless about the happenings on the ground in Ukraine. Meanwhile, the Institute for the Study of War reports Russian operations continue encircling and enveloping Kyiv. Posobiec provides in depth analysis behind biolab facilities, and the Chinese military is searching for a Y-8 reconnaissance aircraft that crashed in the South China Sea earlier this month.

Here’s your Daily dose of Human Events with @JackPosobiec
